AEGIS Configuration File
Copy this to .env and fill in your values

DERIV_API_TOKEN=your_deriv_api_token_here
DERIV_APP_ID=1089

STAKE_USD=10.0
MAX_DAILY_TRADES=3
MAX_DAILY_LOSS_USD=50.0

NEXUS_WS_URL=ws://localhost:9001

MIN_ABSORPTION_VOLUME=500.0
